NOTE# Not in-order
How to use syscall.
	1.) This syscall expects the order to be ./xcipher -p "passphrase" -e/-d inputfile outputfile
		#NOTE: You should specify inputfile and outputfile as ending arguments only.
	2.) You can see how to use system call using ./xcipher -h
